bf29543b4ee00696b68a9900fb38528cf5","tid":1227045,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:09.000Z","msg":"陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236e4b58f73e0c5b4735defb83303d570dec88d0","tid":1227045,"uid":51811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"唉...反送中第一條人命....一路好走"},{"pid":"1fc8f9963735ba9dc831336985838eba898ff7b8","tid":1227045,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ee774df66aee3ed74c99f46a20255281793ff5","tid":1227045,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:58.000Z","msg":"聽日一定要出嚟"},{"pid":"a4346d77d71419d66dd4d40560beda9e98ba2d62","tid":1227045,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe6617d3633a1c931178baaec0929188a6fda25","tid":1227045,"uid":3008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"點解啊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cd391166293aacb2b29e4a5618b1ce36573ef1","tid":1227045,"uid":23931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"班狗要血債血償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c18c2eac535141ae0ab6434027ca63aa2bb7072","tid":1227045,"uid":123050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行政機關濫用權力之審判</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判絞刑。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60jU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60jU2.png&h=0f218e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=af8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909&amp;oe=5D8A89DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daf8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909%26oe%3D5D8A89DA&h=582c6bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24eb3077e38ac3461626100e0441f199ce31bc66","tid":1227045,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa193033fa5fecce603e522c96955883afc76683","tid":1227045,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"HK01? 其他我先信"},{"pid":"23b7322f2f9e6ee2efe535fde7c11f190898f5d1","tid":1227045,"uid":209678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"英雄，如果俾人迫害跳既，一定要搵佢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f283fdc0cc93487d042c321fa5bec7c6569820f","tid":1227045,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96b2ecff9573cffc4757d59efa0a5fb09ff421f4","tid":1227045,"uid":1727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa193033fa5fecce603e522c96955883afc76683","tid":1227045,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"HK01? 其他我先信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fx914R7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFx914R7.png&h=a37f26f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都希望係fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe457e35f8ae7b68dc9c066554db996853603bc","tid":1227045,"uid":36828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7f84a130998bfd2aef225c70924584ef4a8c81","tid":1227045,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c0d78cf7c939c9b245c3360b4a0ef9d1761220","tid":1227045,"uid":170128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"每次見到依啲新聞真係好sad 今次係更加sad!"},{"pid":"be890e976523ca2c1e47a9a26efb4f